      "number": 14,
      "text": "14. 다음은 Java 언어에 대한 문제이다. 아래 코드를 확인하여 알맞는 출력값을 작성하시오.",
      "question_html": "<p data-ke-size=\"size16\" style=\"color: #555555; text-align: start;\"><b>14. 다음은 Java 언어에 대한 문제이다. 아래 코드를 확인하여 알맞는 출력값을 작성하시오.</b></p>",
      "options": "",
      "images": [],
      "code": "class Main {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        int a[] = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9};\n        ODDNumber OE = new ODDNumber();\n        System.out.print(OE.sum(a, true) + \", \" + OE.sum(a, false));\n    }\n}\ninterface Number {\n    int sum(int[] a, boolean odd);\n}\nclass ODDNumber implements Number {\n    public int sum(int[] a, boolean odd) {\n        int result = 0;\n        for(int i=0; i < a.length; i++){\n            if((odd && a[i] % 2 != 0) || (!odd && a[i] % 2 == 0))\n                result += a[i];\n        }\n        return result;\n    }\n}",
      "code_html": "<div class=\"code-line\"><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">class</span> Main {</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">    <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">public</span> <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">static</span> <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">void</span> main(<span style=\"color: #066de2;\">String</span>[] args) {</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">        <span style=\"color: #066de2;\">int</span> a[] <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">=</span> {<span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">1</span>, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">2</span>, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">3</span>, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">4</span>, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">5</span>, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">6</span>, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">7</span>, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">8</span>, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">9</span>};</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">        ODDNumber OE <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">new</span> ODDNumber();</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">        <span style=\"color: #066de2;\">System</span>.<span style=\"color: #066de2;\">out</span>.<span style=\"color: #066de2;\">print</span>(OE.sum(a, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">true</span>) <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">+</span> <span style=\"color: #63a35c;\">\", \"</span> <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">+</span> OE.sum(a, <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">false</span>));</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">    }</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">}</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\"><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">interface</span> Number {</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">    <span style=\"color: #066de2;\">int</span> sum(<span style=\"color: #066de2;\">int</span>[] a, <span style=\"color: #066de2;\">boolean</span> odd);</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">}</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\"><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">class</span> ODDNumber <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">implements</span> Number {</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">    <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">public</span> <span style=\"color: #066de2;\">int</span> sum(<span style=\"color: #066de2;\">int</span>[] a, <span style=\"color: #066de2;\">boolean</span> odd) {</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">        <span style=\"color: #066de2;\">int</span> result <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">0</span>;</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">        <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">for</span>(<span style=\"color: #066de2;\">int</span> i<span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">=</span><span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">0</span>; i <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">&lt;</span> a.<span style=\"color: #066de2;\">length</span>; i<span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">+</span><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">+</span>){</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">            <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">if</span>((odd <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">&amp;</span><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">&amp;</span> a[i] % <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">2</span> <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">!</span><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">0</span>) <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">|</span><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">|</span> (<span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">!</span>odd <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">&amp;</span><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">&amp;</span> a[i] % <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">2</span> <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">=</span><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #0099cc;\">0</span>))</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">                result <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">+</span><span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">=</span> a[i];</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">        }        </div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">        <span style=\"color: #a71d5d;\">return</span> result;</div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">    }    </div>\n<div class=\"code-line\">}</div>",
      "answer": "25, 20",
      "answer_html": "<p data-ke-size=\"size16\" style=\"color: #555555; text-align: start;\">25, 20</p>"
